OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FIt will be at least another ten years
OL,7,Funtil we will be able to catch an HS2
OL,8,Ftrain from Birmingham to London, with
OL,9,Fthe line now not expected to be
OL,10,Fcomplete until 2035 - and coming in
OL,11,Fbillions of pounds over budget.
OL,13,FMore than 44 miles of tunnels have now
OL,14,Fbeen completed, with research
OL,15,Festimating the project could create
OL,16,F30,000 new jobs in the West Midlands.
