OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FHS2 was originally due to run between
OL,7,FLondon and Birmingham, then onto
OL,8,FManchester and Leeds, but the project
OL,9,Fhas been severely curtailed by
OL,10,Fspiralling costs, despite being scaled
OL,11,Fback.
OL,13,FIn Parliament on Wednesday, 18 June,
OL,14,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,15,Fsaid there is "no reasonable way to
OL,16,Fdeliver" the high-speed railway on
OL,17,Fschedule and within budget.
