OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FShe said she will accept all
OL,7,Frecommendations from a review by James
OL,8,FStewart into how HS2 has been managed
OL,9,Fup until now.
OL,11,FIn a statement to Parliament, the
OL,12,FSecretary of State condemned the
OL,13,F"litany of failure" of HS2, citing
OL,14,Fspiralling costs, ineffective
OL,15,Foversight and broken promises.
OL,17,FThe review states: "There is no single
OL,18,Fexplanation for the failings of the
OL,19,FHS2 Programme.
