OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,F"External disruptors (Brexit, the war
OL,7,Fin Ukraine, Covid-19 and a high
OL,8,Finflationary period) have undoubtedly
OL,9,Fhad an impact, but fundamentally a
OL,10,Fcombination of the Government, DfT as
OL,11,FSponsor and Shareholder, HS2 Ltd as
OL,12,Fthe delivery entity, and the private
OL,13,Fsector supply chain have failed to be
OL,14,Fable to deliver a project of the
OL,15,Foriginal scale and size of HS2."
OL,17,FSo, what are some of the main failings
OL,18,Fof the project? Here at ITV News
OL,19,FCentral we have pulled together a list.
OL,21,F1. Cancelled Phase 2
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/17
