OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FThe original route was set to run from
OL,7,FLondon to Birmingham, with two
OL,8,Fseparate legs running from the
OL,9,FMidlands to Leeds,and Manchester.
OL,11,FDue to soaring costs, in 2021, Boris
OL,12,FJohnson announced the scrapping of the
OL,13,FLeeds leg, with Rishi Sunak cancelling
OL,14,Fthe leg to Manchester in 2023.
OL,16,FThe cost of scrapping phase 2 works is
OL,17,Festimated at around #2bn.
OL,19,F2. Delayed completion of Phase 1
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
