OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FAs the opening of Phase 1 to
OL,7,FBirmingham is pushed back further and
OL,8,Ffurther, costs continue to soar.
OL,10,FThe review highlights that without
OL,11,Faction; "Phase 1 alone risks becoming
OL,12,Fone of the most expensive railway
OL,13,Flines in the world - with costs
OL,14,Fballooning by #37 billion".
