OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FWhen the project was first drawn up in
OL,7,F2009, the estimated cost for the
OL,8,Fentire project, including Phase 1 and
OL,9,F2, was #37.5bn. The most recent
OL,10,Ffigures estimate it will cost between
OL,11,F#49bn and #56.6bn, despite the second
OL,12,Fphase being cancelled.
OL,14,F3. Contractors
OL,16,FThe review states that; "HS2 Ltd has
OL,17,Flacked the capability to deal with the
OL,18,Fsize and complexity of the HS2
OL,19,FProgramme."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
