OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FIt goes on to say that the model
OL,7,Fchosen for the project was wrong, but
OL,8,Fthere was a "failure to change course
OL,9,Fwhen problems arose."
OL,11,FExtra costs are also down to problems
OL,12,Fwith some of the building work.
OL,14,FIn November last year, issued were
OL,15,Ffound on some of the bridges built on
OL,16,Fthe line between London and Birmingham.
