OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FSteel firm Severfield identified
OL,7,Fwelding problems on a number of its
OL,8,Fstructures, including nine bridges on
OL,9,Fthe HS2 line, with repair work costing
OL,10,Fmore than #20m to fix.
OL,12,FAt the time, HS2 said: "We have
OL,13,Fidentified a number of welding defects
OL,14,Frelated to steel fabrication work
OL,15,Fundertaken by one of our suppliers.
OL,17,F"This will not impact on the safety or
OL,18,Fquality of the operational railway
OL,19,Fwhich is being designed to the highest
OL,20,Fstandards."
