OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FIn total more than 500 bridges are
OL,7,Fbeing built along the route from
OL,8,FLondon to Curzon Street in Birmingham.
OL,10,F4. Desire to build the best
OL,12,FHS2 was a project sold on speed.
OL,14,FThe promise was trains travelling
OL,15,Fbetween London and Birmingham at
OL,16,Fspeeds of up to 225mph. This meant a
OL,17,Fstraight line was required to be built
OL,18,Fbetween the two cities to ensure speed
OL,19,Fof trains.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
