OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FThe route was to go through the
OL,7,FChilterns AONB, with extensive tunnels
OL,8,Frequired to keep trains out of sight
OL,9,Fand ensure the natural area was
OL,10,Fprotected.
OL,12,FThe scope of the plans kept changing,
OL,13,Fdriving up costs. Pressure from
OL,14,Fprotestors and constituents left MPs
OL,15,Fvoting to increase the tunnel length
OL,16,Fthrough the Chilterns, in turn costing
OL,17,Fmore money.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
