OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FThe review found many key decisions
OL,7,Fhave been driven by schedule rather
OL,8,Fthan cost, stating: "Pressure from
OL,9,Fpoliticians to maintain momentum, fear
OL,10,Fof HS2 being cancelled, and the belief
OL,11,Fthat costs will increase as a result
OL,12,Fof delay have featured strongly."
OL,14,F5. Pace of decision making
OL,16,FSince it was initially approved in
OL,17,F2012, the HS2 project has been through
OL,18,FBrexit, a global pandemic and seven
OL,19,Fdifferent Prime Ministers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
