OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FThe James Stewart review highlights
OL,7,Fthe pace of decision making as one of
OL,8,Fthe main disruptors for the project,
OL,9,Fwith no buffer in place for politics.
OL,11,FIt says: "Any project of this size and
OL,12,Fscale delivered across multiple
OL,13,Fdecades is going to be impacted by
OL,14,Fpolitics.
OL,16,F"When I looked at comparator projects
OL,17,F` Tideway, Sizewell C, even Crossrail
OL,18,F` there was a buffer to the politics,
OL,19,Feither with external shareholders,
OL,20,Fregulators or joint sponsors.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
