OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,F"The HS2 Programme has had no such
OL,7,Fbuffers and has been subject to
OL,8,Fevolving political aims, which pushed
OL,9,Fforward on the schedule before there
OL,10,Fwas sufficient design maturity and
OL,11,Fcaused progressive removals of scope."
OL,13,FThe review found trust between
OL,14,Fstakeholders needs to be restored as
OL,15,Fthe project moves forward.
OL,17,FIt says: "The significant and
OL,18,Fconsistent cost overruns that have
OL,19,Fbeen a feature of the project have
OL,20,Fundermined trust in HS2."
