OL,3,CFive ways HS2 has wasted money as
OL,4,Cgovernment announces further delays
OL,6,FFollowing the publishing of the
OL,7,Freview, the Transport Secretary, Heidi
OL,8,FAlexander, said: "This must be a line
OL,9,Fin the sand. This government is
OL,10,Fdelivering HS2 from Birmingham to
OL,11,FLondon after years of mismanagement,
OL,12,Fflawed reporting and ineffective
OL,13,Foversight.
OL,15,F"Mark Wild and Mike Brown were part of
OL,16,Fthe team, with me, that turned
OL,17,FCrossrail into the Elizabeth Line ` we
OL,18,Fhave done it before, we will do it
OL,19,Fagain.
