OL,6,F"Passengers and taxpayers deserve new
OL,7,Frailways the country can be proud of
OL,8,Fand the work to get HS2 back on track
OL,9,Fis firmly underway. "
OL,11,FThe Transport Secretary confirmed Mike
OL,12,FBrown will be taking over as HS2 Ltd
OL,13,FChair, working alongside CEO Mark Wild
OL,14,Fto deliver a programme reset,
OL,15,Fincluding reviewing the costs and
OL,16,Fschedule, renegotiating HS2's large
OL,17,Fconstruction contracts, and reviewing
OL,18,FHS2 Ltd's skills and structure.
